            <div class="opener__topic-title-dek-wrapper ">

                    <span class="opener__topics ">
            <a class="opener__topics-link " href="https://www.propublica.org/topics/trump-administration">Trump Administration</a>
        </span>
    
    <h1 class="opener__hed " >        What Donald Trump’s Criminal Trial Reveals About a Potential Second Trump Administration
    </h1>

    <h2 class="opener__dek " >        The picture that emerged in the New York courtroom was of a person on top of details, aware of what his team is doing. Along with outside events, it suggests Trump will be even less constricted by rules and norms than he was before.
    </h2>

    </div> <!-- Close .opener__topic-title-dek-wrapper -->

</div>
        
<div class="article-meta-1
