        <div class="promo-donate-2__bg">
            <svg width="265" height="157" viewBox="0 0 265 157" preserveAspectRatio="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M133.852 0L0 79.344 133.852 157 265 79.344 133.852 0z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <p class="promo-donate-1__text">Summer Member Drive: Protect journalism that holds power to account.</p>
        <a class="promo-donate-2__btn | btn" style="--button-color: var(--red-50)" href="https://give.propublica.org/give/346423/#!/donation/checkout?c_src=InL">Donate Now</a>
